Hmm, by the way,

00:19:17.907 --> 00:19:19.158
I hope you realize…

00:19:20.368 --> 00:19:23.329
a candidate without approval
from the US could never get elected

00:19:23.412 --> 00:19:24.914
as the president of South Korea,

