No, no, leave 'em on for now.

00:40:04.652 --> 00:40:06.905
…my years in America,
studying with the Korean flag

00:40:06.988 --> 00:40:08.239
on the wall above me,

00:40:08.323 --> 00:40:13.661
all the way to the very tragic death
of my husband Jang Junik

00:40:13.745 --> 00:40:15.788
who fought for peace and reunification,

00:40:16.539 --> 00:40:21.002
and up until this day,
when I almost was killed on that train.

