Some say that I shouldn't be
running for president

00:40:43.858 --> 00:40:46.945
with the party of my late husband.

00:40:47.028 --> 00:40:49.948
And some say I'm not fit
to lead this nation

00:40:50.031 --> 00:40:52.575
because I spent most of my life
out of Korea.

